1. *Sekundu* mu je trebalo da odgovori na pitanje. (It took him a second to answer the question.)
2. On je ušao u sobu za samo *sekundu*. (He entered the room for just a second.)
3. Ona je zagledala u njega *sekundu*. (She stared at him for a second.)
4. *Sekundu* sam mislio da je to on. (I thought it was him for a second.)
5. Ona se zastala na *sekundu*. (She paused for a second.)
6. On je skočio u vazduh na *sekundu*. (He jumped in the air for a second.)